{"tid":1387160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每個禮拜有幾十人被告暴動罪真係元氣大傷, 可否轉換一下抗爭方法","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:18:28.000Z","uid":281070,"like":52,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2da73fba510d7170dc80483527f178d36a7a1e53","tid":1387160,"uid":281070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:06:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>以後不要再堵路, 不要再死守一地, 可否轉換一下方式, 例如快閃行動? 或者大家想想有無其他方式, 總之再係咁落去真係唔係辦法。必須記住三大原則:不被捕, 不受傷, 不流血, 大家幾嬲都好, 千祁千祁唔好放棄呢三大原則</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6ad766749a0d7a58f0f0c5e8bc988d43d94baa58","tid":1387160,"uid":66324,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"主要問題係太戀戰姐, 其他無乜野"},{"pid":"22d20eab657d1491f4209e1def3075a38b700253","tid":1387160,"uid":64743,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"我今朝已經出post 講過<br />\n冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3375a72398ac3052db5fc65683e6feafdcf3c8f9","tid":1387160,"uid":131282,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:08:19.000Z","msg":"[個腦生屎？] 咪撚再講捐飯 、捐八達通  用下個腦啦 不服來辯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n香港人全部都係弱智<br />\n竟然唔從根本解決問題 買裝比前線<br />\n重話香港人好醒😨<br />\n有鬼帶頭吹風搞捐飯捐券捐錢比d不知名人士就跟<br />\n<br />\non99<br />\n#恥而為伍"},{"pid":"0a1cf48797c94f77c1320fbc870d0a6d102a441f","tid":1387160,"uid":199590,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">永遠支持前線決定</span></span><br />\n<br />\n重申多一次，唔明點解前線要留既請入，前線只會係以下三種情況下徹退。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"643cbb43df509d2706b054d63087a8f5451c9bd7","tid":1387160,"uid":281070,"like